{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6c5e79760f","title":"毛泽东在中央常委会上的四点指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aae22688e5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"6c5e79760f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d597e3e1b3","type":"title","text":"在中央常委会上的四点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6c5e79760f"},{"id":"1be2273459","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6c5e79760f"},{"id":"3d2c9cabc5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1） 大家要挺身而出，同群众见面，接受群众的批评。要进行自我批评，引火烧身。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6c5e79760f"},{"id":"d40d0a8f03","type":"paragraph","text":"（2） 大家要挺身而出，向群众解释党的政策，被戴高帽子，抹了黑脸的，洗洗脸继续上班工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6c5e79760f"},{"id":"f15b080ce9","type":"paragraph","text":"（3） 从长远利益出发，团结多数。牛鬼蛇神就是地、富、反、坏、右，是少数。有些人就是犯了严重错误，也得挽救他，使他改过自新，不然怎么团结百分之九十五以上呢？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6c5e79760f"},{"id":"ffa56d39a9","type":"paragraph","text":"（4） 说服干部，使干部懂得不要人人过关，都搞得灰溜溜的。两个挺身而出，不能躲躲闪闪，怕字当头。敢字当头，再大的问题也能解决。怕字当头，价钱越来越高。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6c5e79760f"}],"page":{"id":"7070e056b8","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6c5e79760f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}